2016-08-21 20-00-00:
	Title: Registrations now open for RA:GL Season 2!
	Author: Oliver Brakmann
	Content: After the very successful first season, season 2 of the Red Alert Global League will kick off on September 5th!\n\nPublic registrations are now open until August 31st, so don't hold off too long to get your name in! With a prize pool of over $500, it will be well worth your time.\n\nVisit the OpenRA homepage (http://openra.net) to find all the links to the league's rules and registrations forum threads, and also to read about what the OpenRA developers have been up to over the last few months!\n\nWe wish all participants good luck and a lot of fun!
